drop index 拥有账户_PK on OwnAccount;


alter table OwnAccount
drop foreign key FK_OWNACCOU_拥有账户_CLIENT;

alter table OwnAccount
drop foreign key FK_OWNACCOU_拥有账户2_ACCOUNT;

drop table if exists OwnAccount;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: OwnAccount */
/*==============================================================*/
create table OwnAccount
(
client_id varchar(20) not null comment '',
account_id varchar(50) not null comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: 拥有账户_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index 拥有账户_PK on OwnAccount
(
client_id,
account_id
);

alter table OwnAccount add constraint FK_OWNACCOU_拥有账户_CLIENT foreign key (client_id)
references client (client_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table OwnAccount add constraint FK_OWNACCOU_拥有账户2_ACCOUNT foreign key (account_id)
references account (account_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
